dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents addresses for Iowa County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Iowa_Addresses_2015.gdb'. [This point based shapefile represent the address point layer for Iowa County, WIS]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [This data set was produced to be used with Bullberry Systems, Inc, R3GIS emergency routing software, but can be used in any mapping software that is built on an ESRI platform utilizing shapefiles.]
